Ranch Powder

¼ c buttermilk powder
1½ tbsp onion powder
½ tbsp dried chives
½ tbsp dried parsley
½ tbsp dried dill
½ tbsp garlic powder
2 tsp kosher salt

In a medium bowl, whisk together all of the ingredients. Use right away with any dish of your choosing or store in an airtight container in your pantry.
